OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has pledged to meet its
OL,7,Fflagging postal delivery targets by
OL,8,Fthe middle of next year as it
OL,9,Fannounced a #500 million investment
OL,10,Fand the rollout of changes to scrap
OL,11,Fsecond-class post on Saturdays.
OL,13,FThe group said it would begin to phase
OL,14,Fin a new letter delivery model
OL,15,Fnationwide, which will see it deliver
OL,16,Fsecond-class post every other weekday
OL,17,Fonly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
