OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FIt follows an agreement with the
OL,7,FCommunication Workers Union (CWU) last
OL,8,Fweek, bringing an end to a lengthy
OL,9,Fdispute over the second-class post
OL,10,Foverhaul.
OL,12,FRoyal Mail said the changes and
OL,13,Fplanned investment will see it improve
OL,14,Ffirst-class, next-day delivery to
OL,15,Faround 85% within nine months of the
OL,16,Freforms being brought in, before
OL,17,Freaching the 90% target set by
OL,18,Fregulator Ofcom within a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FThe firm also vowed to deliver 93% of
OL,7,Fsecond-class letters in three days
OL,8,Fwithin the space of nine months, and
OL,9,Fhit the 95% target by May next year.
OL,11,FRegulator Ofcom said Royal Mail must
OL,12,Fnow "get on and implement" its
OL,13,Fimprovement plan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
