OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FRoyal Mail ` whose owner International
OL,7,FDistribution Services was bought last
OL,8,Fyear by Czech billionaire Daniel
OL,9,FKretinsky ` was fined a record #21
OL,10,Fmillion by Ofcom in October for
OL,11,Fmissing targets after it delivered
OL,12,Fjust 77% of first-class post and 92.5%
OL,13,Fof second-class post on time in 2024-
OL,14,F25.
OL,16,FFrom April 1, Ofcom lowered the
OL,17,Fdelivery targets for first-class post
OL,18,Fto be delivered the next day from 93%
OL,19,Fto 90% and second-class to be
OL,20,Fdelivered within three days from 98.5%
OL,21,Fto 95%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FBut Ofcom added a new "enforceable"
OL,7,Fbackstop delivery target, so that 99%
OL,8,Fof mail has to be delivered no more
OL,9,Fthan two days late.
OL,11,FRoyal Mail said its #500 million
OL,12,Finvestment in the service over the
OL,13,Fnext five years included an agreement
OL,14,Fto allow around 6,000 part-time postal
OL,15,Fworkers to increase their average
OL,16,Fweekly hours if needed as part of the
OL,17,Fsecond-class post reforms.
OL,19,FIt will be funded by savings made from
OL,20,Fthe changes to the Universal Service.
OL,26,@nD@WOUnD@cO]
