OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FAlistair Cochrane, chief executive of
OL,7,FRoyal Mail, said: "We recognise our
OL,8,Fservice hasn't always been the
OL,9,Fstandard our customers rightly expect
OL,10,Fand we're determined to do better.
OL,12,F"The plan we've set out today shows
OL,13,Fhow we'll make a step change in
OL,14,Fperformance across the UK, backed by
OL,15,F#500 million of investment over the
OL,16,Fnext five years."
OL,18,FIt comes after Ofcom said it had been
OL,19,Fpushing for a "credible plan for
OL,20,Fchange, backed by investment".
OL,26,@oD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
