PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776791154
OL,3,CRoyal Mail announces #500m plan to
OL,4,Cmeet flagging delivery targets
OL,6,FNatalie Black, Ofcom's group director
OL,7,Ffor infrastructure and connectivity,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Now that's published, Royal
OL,9,FMail needs to get on and implement it.
OL,11,F"Their plan must deliver significant
OL,12,Fand continuous improvement, with
OL,13,Fperformance getting back on track."
OL,15,FOfcom last year gave the green light
OL,16,Fto Royal Mail's plans to scale back
OL,17,Fsecond-class letter deliveries,
OL,18,Fstarting from July 28, while keeping
OL,19,Fthe first-class and parcels service
OL,20,Funchanged.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
